
1. Deep copies the entire array in to a new one.
   char [][] visitedArr = Arrays.stream(grid).map(char[]::clone).toArray(char[][]::new);

2. Converting a 2d array into 1d array through flatenning and passing each row into stream and filtering out any requirement.
   Arrays.stream(grid).flatMapToInt(x -> Arrays.stream(x)).anyMatch(val -> val==1);

3. Fill Arrays : Arrays.fill(in_degree, 0);
